nodes.text: Overseer Brynn was a female Human who served as an officer within the ranks of the Imperial Military during the Galactic Civil War. Brynn was assigned to command an Imperial spaceport control center in the settlement Mos Shuuta on the planet Tatooine and shortly after the Battle of Yavin, she encountered a band of fugitives who were on the run from the Hutt crime lord Teemo and had infiltrated the control center in an attempt to release the docking clamps on the YT-1300 light freighter Krayt Fang. The fugitives escaped Tatooine, but returned a short time later to confront Teemo, and they encountered Overseer Brynn once again.
